highlights.text: “Made You Look” by Meghan Trainor is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 110 spots at #33.
Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Anti-Hero” is the highest at #1.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 300 weeks straight.
“Lift Me Up - From Black Panther: Wakanda Forever - Music From and Inspired By” by Rihanna is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #11.
